link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1279786%26csid%3D261_341&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=065485f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279786&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n疫情進一步受控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}